Quatrefages, 1866 | 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Nereididae" genus="Nereis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nereis splendida" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="splendida">Nereis splendida</taxonomicName>
Grube, 1840
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="20997">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="20997">
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Nereididae" genus="Nereis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nereis falsa" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="falsa">Nereis falsa</taxonomicName>
is considered a synonym of 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Nereididae" genus="Nereis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nereis splendida" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="splendida">Nereis splendida</taxonomicName>
Grube, 1840 by 
<bibRefCitation author="Nunez, J" editor="Vieitez, J. M." journalOrPublisher="Museo Nacional de Ciencias Naturales, CA, SAIC, Madrid" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" title="Annelida, Polychaeta I. In: Ramos MA, Alba J, Belles X, Gosalbez J, Guerra A, Macpherson E, Martin F, Serrano J, Templado J (Eds.) Fauna Iberica" year="2004">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Núñez">Nunez</normalizedToken>
(2004)
</bibRefCitation>
. However, a 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Nereididae" genus="Nereis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nereis splendida" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="splendida">Nereis splendida</taxonomicName>
Blainville, 1825 also exists in literature and in online databases (e.g. WoRMS) which should take priority over Grube's species and render the latter a junior homonym. 
<bibRefCitation author="Gravina, Maria Flavia" journalOrPublisher="Atti della Societa Toscana di Scienze Naturali Memorie Serie. B" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="147 - 164" title="The genus Nereis L., 1758 (Polychaeta, Nereididae): State of the art for identification of Mediterranean species" volume="122" year="2015">Gravina et al. (2015)</bibRefCitation>
therefore use 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Nereididae" genus="Nereis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nereis falsa" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="falsa">Nereis falsa</taxonomicName>
as the valid name, as 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Nereididae" genus="Nereis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nereis splendida" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="splendida">Nereis splendida</taxonomicName>
Grube, although having priority over 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Nereididae" genus="Nereis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nereis falsa" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="falsa">Nereis falsa</taxonomicName>
Quatrefages, is pre-occupied. However, the identity of the species described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Blainville, Henri de" journalOrPublisher="FG Levrault, Strasbourg and Paris" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" title="Dictionnaire des Sciences naturelles, dans lequel on traite methodiquement des differens etres de la nature, consideres soit en eux-memes, d'apres l'etat actuel de nos connaisance, soit relativement a l'utilite qu'en peuvent retirer la medicine, l'agriculture, le commerce et les artes" year="1825">Blainville (1825)</bibRefCitation>
species is confused and early authors (e.g. 
<bibRefCitation author="Quatrefages, Armand de" journalOrPublisher="Librarie Encyclopedique de Roret, Paris" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" title="Histoire naturelle des Anneles marins et d'eau douce. Annelides et Gephyriens" year="1866">Quatrefages 1866</bibRefCitation>
:434, 
<bibRefCitation author="Rathke, Heinrich" journalOrPublisher="Nova Acta der Kaiserlichen Leopold-Carolin Deutschen Akademie der Naturforscher, Halle" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="1 - 264" title="Beitraege zur Fauna Norwegens" volume="20" year="1843">Rathke 1843</bibRefCitation>
:172) consider it indeterminable and probably belonging to 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Nephtyidae" genus="Nephtys" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nephtys" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">Nephtys</taxonomicName>
. In addition, 
<bibRefCitation author="Blainville, Henri de" journalOrPublisher="FG Levrault, Strasbourg and Paris" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" title="Dictionnaire des Sciences naturelles, dans lequel on traite methodiquement des differens etres de la nature, consideres soit en eux-memes, d'apres l'etat actuel de nos connaisance, soit relativement a l'utilite qu'en peuvent retirer la medicine, l'agriculture, le commerce et les artes" year="1825">Blainville (1825)</bibRefCitation>
creates a confusing situation of synonyms by applying the name 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Nereididae" genus="Nereis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nereis splendida" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="splendida">Nereis splendida</taxonomicName>
to a specimen he had received from Dr. Leach under the (probably unpublished) name 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Nereididae" genus="Nereis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nereis clava" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="clava">Nereis clava</taxonomicName>
(p. 439) and in the same publication transfers 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Hesionidae" genus="Hesione" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hesione splendida" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="splendida">Hesione splendida</taxonomicName>
Savigny 1818 to 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Nereididae" genus="Nereis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nereis" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">Nereis</taxonomicName>
, creating an unresolved synonymy with 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Nereididae" genus="Nereis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nereis splendida" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="splendida">Nereis splendida</taxonomicName>
(p. 443). Until this confusion is resolved, the name 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Nereididae" genus="Nereis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nereis falsa" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="falsa">Nereis falsa</taxonomicName>
is used here, following 
<bibRefCitation author="Gravina, Maria Flavia" journalOrPublisher="Atti della Societa Toscana di Scienze Naturali Memorie Serie. B" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="147 - 164" title="The genus Nereis L., 1758 (Polychaeta, Nereididae): State of the art for identification of Mediterranean species" volume="122" year="2015">Gravina et al. (2015)</bibRefCitation>
. See also 
<bibRefCitation author="Salazar-Vallejo, Sergio Ignacio" journalOrPublisher="Revista de Biologia Tropical" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="847 - 857" title="How false is Nereisfalsa? (Annelida, Phyllodocida, Nereididae)" volume="65" year="2017">Salazar-Vallejo et al. (2017)</bibRefCitation>
and discussions on the Annelida mailing list for extensive clarifications on the identity and nomenclatural problems associated with 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Nereididae" genus="Nereis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nereis falsa" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="falsa">Nereis falsa</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Nereididae" genus="Nereis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nereis splendida" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="splendida">Nereis splendida</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
